Type: Package
Package: gigg
Title: Group Inverse-Gamma Gamma Shrinkage for Sparse Regression with Grouping Structure
Version: 0.2.1
Description: This package implements a Gibbs sampler corresponding to a Group 
    Inverse-Gamma Gamma (GIGG) regression model with adjustment covariates. 
    Hyperparameters in the GIGG prior specification can either be fixed by the 
    user or can be estimated via Marginal Maximum Likelihood Estimation.
    <arXiv:2102.10670>.
